window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From USA Today Bestselling author Brynne Asher comes a single-mom, protective-hero romantic suspense where he falls first.</p> <p>My son and I are in danger. The life and death kind. The kind that forces me to make choices no mother should have to.</p> <p>I’ll do anything to keep my son safe and not sacrifice my responsibility to my patients.</p> <p>I’m desperate.</p> <p>Desperate enough to beg broody Special Agent Micah Emmett for help. But he has a job, and it doesn’t include protecting me. Why should he? He doesn’t know me.</p> <p>Or so I thought.</p> <p>Because you can learn a lot about another person when they’re being tapped. And Micah has been watching me for a long time.</p> <p>Now the special agent is glued to my side.</p> <p>And I've been tapped in more ways than one.</p>"; 
